      • AlcoholData

        public AlcoholData(int aid,
                   java.lang.String name,
                   java.lang.String appellation,
                   java.lang.String sulfiteDescription,
                   double alchContent,
                   java.lang.String netContent,
                   java.lang.String healthWarning,

                   int classType,
                   java.lang.String labelLegibility,
                   java.lang.String labelSize,
                   java.lang.String formulas,
                   int alcoholType,
                   java.lang.String bottlersInfo,
                   java.lang.String brandName,
                   java.lang.String status,
                   int wineVintage,
                   double phLevel,
                   java.lang.String grapeVarietal,
                   java.lang.String infoOnBottle,
                   java.lang.String sourceOfProduct,
                   java.sql.Date dateApproved,
                   int originCode)
        Creates an AlcoholData object.
        Parameters:
        aid - Account ID linked to the object.
        name - Fanciful name of the alcohol.
        appellation - For wines, the area of origination for the alcohol.
        sulfiteDescription - Description of the sulfite content of the alcohol.
        alchContent - Proof of the alcohol.
        netContent - Net alcohol content.
        healthWarning - Text of the alcohol's label's health warning.
        productType - Type of product.
        classType - Type of class of the alcohol.
        labelLegibility - Metric for legibility of the label.
        labelSize - Actual size of the label.
        formulas - Formulas for the alcoholic beverage.
        alcoholType - Type of alcohol.
        bottlersInfo - General information about the bottler.
        brandName - Brand name for the alcohol.
        status - Status of the alcohol.
        wineVintage - Vintage year for the wine.
        phLevel - Level of pH in the alcohol.
        grapeVarietal - Varieties of grape used in the wine.
        infoOnBottle - Information listed on label.
        sourceOfProduct - Location from whence the product came.
        dateApproved - Date alcohol was approved for sale.
        originCode - Code for state the alcohol originates from.
